# Slide 3

```{r, include=FALSE}
library(tidyverse)
library(here)
```

```{r, echo=FALSE, message=FALSE, out.width="100%", fig.height=5, fig.retina=2, dpi=300}
mtcars %>%
  ggplot() +
  aes(x = wt, y = mpg) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth(method = lm) +
  theme_classic()
```

