# A table

.Large[]
```{r, message=F}
read_csv(file = here("data", "tidy", "mtcars_tidy.csv")) %>%
  mutate_if(is.numeric, round, digits = 2) %>%
  arrange(cyl) %>%
  knitr::kable()
```






